text: Luna Papa (Russian: Лунный папа) is a 1999 Tajik Russian comedy movie. Bakhtyar Khudojnazarov directed the movie. Chulpan Khamatova, Mortiz Bleibtreu, Merab Ninidze, Nikolay Fomenko, Dinmukhamet Akhimov, and Sherali Abdulkajsov starred in it. ==Other websites== * Category:1999 comedy movies Category:Tajik movies Category:Russian comedy movies Category:German comedy movies Category:Japanese comedy movies Category:Austrian comedy movies Category:Swiss comedy movies Category:French comedy movies Category:Uzbekistani movies Category:Movies directed by Bakhtyar Khudojnazarov
